    • Method Detail

      • getVisitedPlatformsIdx

        public final int getVisitedPlatformsIdx()
        Retrieves the index for the Visited Platforms custom dimension in Google Analytics. This index must be configured in the AndroidManifest.xml property named ga.VISITED_PLATFORMS_DIM_IDX, and should match the custom dimension index used in your Google Analytics property configuration. If the field is omitted, a default value of 0 is used, which is ignored by Google Analytics.
        Returns:
        the index for Visited Platforms custom dimension
